# Native projects are generated by Continuous Native Generation (expo prebuild /
# expo run / EAS). Keeping them out of git lets the expo-notifications config
# plugin set aps-environment=production for release builds instead of shipping a
# stale committed `development` value. Regenerate locally with `npx expo prebuild`.
